                <fr:addr type="user">//erct/erct-000Y</fr:addr>
                <fr:route>foreign-erct-erct-000Y.xml</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Section-retraction pair">Section-retraction pair</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
                <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-000Y.agda" type="external">erct-000Y.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s \colon  B \to  A]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r \colon  A \to  B]]></fr:tex> be a pair of maps. A homotopy <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[h \colon  r\circ  s \sim  1_{B}]]></fr:tex> exhibits <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex> as a <fr:em><fr:strong>section</fr:strong></fr:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r]]></fr:tex> and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r]]></fr:tex> as a <fr:em><fr:strong>retraction</fr:strong></fr:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s]]></fr:tex>. Together, 
 <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathopen {}\left \lparen s,r\right \rparen \mathclose {}]]></fr:tex>
 are referred to as a <fr:em><fr:strong>section-retraction pair</fr:strong></fr:em>.</fr:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="foreign-erct-jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="//erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
                  <fr:month>12</fr:month>
                  <fr:day>27</fr:day>
                </fr:date>
                <fr:anchor>3192</fr:anchor>
                <fr:addr type="user">//erct/erct-0025</fr:addr>
                <fr:route>foreign-erct-erct-0025.xml</fr:route>
                <fr:title text="Retract">Retract</fr:title>
                <fr:taxon>Definition</fr:taxon>
                <fr:meta name="source">
  
  
  <fr:link href="https://git.sr.ht/~jonsterling/agda-erct/tree/main/item/agda/erct-0025.agda" type="external">erct-0025.agda</fr:link>
</fr:meta>
              </fr:frontmatter>
              <fr:mainmatter>
                <fr:p>When <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[s\colon  A\to  B]]></fr:tex> is a section of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[r\colon  B\to  A]]></fr:tex>, we say that <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[A]]></fr:tex> is a <fr:em><fr:strong>retract</fr:strong></fr:em> of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[B]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
              </fr:mainmatter>
            </fr:tree>
            <fr:tree show-metadata="false">
              <fr:frontmatter>
                <fr:authors>
                  <fr:author>
                    <fr:link href="foreign-erct-jonmsterling.xml" title="Jon Sterling" addr="//erct/jonmsterling" type="local">Jon Sterling</fr:link>
                  </fr:author>
                </fr:authors>
                <fr:date>
                  <fr:year>2023</fr:year>
